<br>
The idea is to use no drop armour pieces that you no longer use and be able to either modify them using tradeskills or use them in quests to gain other things.<br>
<br>
An example of this would be the Carmine robe that is sitting in my bank. I no longer use it as i've upgraded, now instead of having my former robe collect dust why not use it to create an item that i do need (say Carmine gloves).<br>
<br>
